en.codex: A set of ceremonial daggers from the Orokin era, the Fang Prime's blades resonate violently as they strike. This allows them to pierce hardened materials like armor with ease.
en.description: Fang Prime features a higher base damage than Fang as well as a faster attack speed. The Fang Prime was added into the game in Update 9.0.

ru.description: Набор ритуальных кинжалов из эры Орокин, Клыки Прайм сильно вибрирует с каждым ударом. Это позволяет им с легкостью пробивать любую броню.
